{"_id":"r4c6e1NYXULzjIBY","name":"Particle Beam Bolter","permission":{"default":0,"qHi89sFcK4gHlOPd":3},"type":"beamWeapon","data":{"description":"<p>This weapon shoots a bolt of accelerated particles at near light speed that transfer massive amounts of kinetic energy to the target, superheating and creating an explosion when striking. The bolter&rsquo;s beam is not diffused by the cloud that occurs when it strikes, and so it has greater penetration than the laser pulser. Likewise, the bolter is not affected by smoke, fog, or rain. Bolters must be set for either atmospheric or exoatmospheric (vacuum) operation and will not function in the opposite environment, though it only takes a complex action to switch. The beam appears like an arc of lightning in atmosphere, but is invisible in vacuum (though visible in the shooter&rsquo;s entoptics).</p>","reference":"Eclipse Phase Second Edition p. 208","complexity":"major","restricted":true,"quality":"average","concealable":false,"fragile":false,"singleUse":false,"twoHanded":true,"fixed":false,"long":true,"noClose":false,"noPointBlank":false,"steady":false,"blueprint":{"blueprintType":"","cracked":false,"used":false},"idealUserSize":"","itemSize":"verySmall","accessories":["safetySystem","smartlink"],"ammo":{"charge":25,"max":25,"recharge":0},"primaryAttack":{"armorPiercing":false,"armorRemoving":false,"attackTraits":["knockdown"],"damageFormula":"2d10 + 6","firingModes":["semiAuto","burstFire"],"label":"","notes":"","areaEffect":"","areaEffectRadius":1},"range":50,"secondaryAttack":{"armorPiercing":false,"armorRemoving":false,"attackTraits":[],"damageFormula":"","firingModes":["semiAuto"],"label":"","notes":"","areaEffect":"","areaEffectRadius":1},"state":{"equipped":false},"wareType":""},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.m2ZaPe26xSg2Nhf0"}},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
